Encode envelope and sound parameters in the URL

State changes update the URL via history.replaceState with
?env=N,T,...,ALD&sound=C,A,P,D, mirroring the BASIC syntax. On page
load the params are parsed back into state, so copying the URL bar
gives a shareable link that reproduces the exact envelope and SOUND
parameters. Malformed or missing params fall back to defaults.
